## Overview 
I am a male human that runs a frontend of English and a backend of Consciousness. I am currently using the Earth framework, though this could change in the future.
  
## Installation 
Installation can be done in any Universe®, but if your Universe® isn't configured correctly you may have to go through the 13 000 000 000 year installation process again.
Otherwise, make sure you have the dependencies Human Race, and Civilization installed, then locate the 2 correct entities to use as my source code. 
  
## Compiling
Basic compilation only takes ~9 months, but if you want to have a full production build, it may take a few decades.
 
## Running
To access me, make an english statement such as "hey", or "you wanna talk for a bit?".
